data.description: Introducing a gorgeous contemporary 1-bedroom, 1-bath condo with garage parking and its own private patio backing to majestic trees that embodies the epitome of modern living, nestled in the heart of Bethesda, Maryland. Located in The Kenwood condominium with an abundance of amenities, this stunning residence promises a lifestyle of comfort, elegance, and convenience. ****** As you step into this renovated condo with 1,040 square feet of living space, you are greeted by the timeless beauty of warm hardwood floors that flow seamlessly throughout the open-concept living space. The spacious living room is filled with natural light with sliding glass doors granting access to a large private patio backing to trees—seamlessly blending indoor and outdoor living and simple relaxation. The dining room offers plenty of space for all occasions, while the open atmosphere facilitates spending time with family and friends.  The kitchen is sure to please boasting exquisite granite countertops that provide both durability and an air of sophistication. These countertops offer ample space for meal preparation, and their natural patterns and shimmering surface add a touch of opulence to the space. To complement the granite countertops, the kitchen features an abundance of upgraded cabinetry and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, including a sleek refrigerator, gas range, dishwasher, and microwave. These appliances are not only visually appealing but also deliver exceptional performance, making cooking and meal preparation an absolute pleasure. ****** The bedroom is a peaceful sanctuary, featuring ample space for relaxation and rest. Natural light pours in through large windows, casting a soft glow across the hardwood floors. The serene and tranquil ambiance creates the perfect setting for a good night's sleep, while the large walk-in closet ensures loads of storage space. The bathroom is equally impressive, with a chic modern vessel sink vanity, and sleek fixtures and finishes that elevate your daily routine. An assigned garage parking space and ALL UTILITIES included in the condo fee completes the comfort and convenience of this wonderful home. ****** Enjoy the amenities such as 24/7 concierge and security, outdoor pool, walking paths, picnic and grilling areas, fitness center, party and meeting room, laundry facility on each floor, business center and more! Commuters will appreciate the easy access to major commuting routes and including Friendship Heights Metro just blocks away! Everyone will enjoy the abundance of diverse shopping, dining, and entertainment choices in every direction including Whole Foods Market and Clyde’s of Chevy Chase. For a fabulous home in a vibrant location, look no further, you have found it!
